196
00:18:55,780 --> 00:18:58,930
- Poďme sa na to pozrieť. 
- Dobre.

197
00:19:03,860 --> 00:19:05,920
Pán Oh Hee Min?

198
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:12,710
Detektívka Kim So Kyung, 
z policajnej stanice v Gangname.

199
00:19:19,310 --> 00:19:25,560
